metadata.name: HANS - FKK
metadata.description:
HANS - FKK is the fourth and last piece of the HANS
collection #1.

Collection - 1 is called "Germany in the 40s" - The good the bad and the ugly.

HANS - FKK is piece 4 of 4 and is showing the naturist culture in Germany.

The collection is a collaboration of 3D artists Marqui√±o & Inctube.

HANS is a character we've designed and who will be be available in future collections as well.

The simple design can be interpreted in several ways. Although HANS is a masculine name, HANS can also be a woman. HANS is a pseudonym and placeholder for all people.
